nodes.text: Mawbo Kem was the owner of the reasonably disreputable Mawbo's Performance Hall in Mos Espa on Tatooine. She was well-known among the locals for having many lovers.
In 8 ABY Mawbo Kem hosted an auction in her performance hall, at which one of the items for sale was the famous Alderaan moss painting Killik Twilight.
